body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting Evans Automotive. My name is Raymond Evans. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hi, my name is Cheryl Allen.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Cheryl. How may I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I have some concerns about the privacy of my personal information.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand your worries. To help you better, may I have your date of birth and your address to verify your account?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure. My date of birth is the fifteenth of June, nine six seven eight. And my address is one two three Main Street, City Center.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Got it, Cheryl. Thank you for providing that information. Is there anything else you would like to share regarding your privacy concerns?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's all for now. I just wanted to ensure my information is secure.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Cheryl, for reaching out to us. I will make sure your concerns are addressed. Thank you for your time.
